---
import GlowText from '../ui/GlowText.astro';
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
import styles from './AboutSection.module.css';
---

<section id="about" class={`${styles.section} scroll-reveal`}>
  <GlowText as="h2" size="medium" color="purple" class={styles.sectionTitle}>
    ABOUT ME
  </GlowText>
  <div class={styles.content}>
    <p class={styles.summary}>
      I put 14+ years of professional engineering experience to work building websites for small
      businesses across Denver, Lakewood, and the Colorado Front Range. By day I'm a Staff
      Engineer at Kasa. On the side, I help local businesses get online with sites that are fast,
      look great on every device, and actually show up in search results.
    </p>
    <p class={styles.summary}>
      You get the same tools and standards I use in enterprise software, applied to your
      business site. No templates, no page builders. Just clean, custom code built by someone
      you can <a href="/services/" class="neon-text-orange">meet for coffee</a> and talk to directly.
    </p>
    <p class={styles.summary}>
      I handle everything: design, development, SEO setup, hosting, and ongoing support.
      One person, one point of contact, no handoffs. Whether you need a new site from scratch
      or a redesign of something that isn't working, I'll give you an honest assessment of
      what it takes and what it costs.
    </p>
    <div class={styles.highlights}>
      <div class={styles.highlight}>
        <span class={styles.highlightValue}>14+</span>
        <span class={styles.highlightLabel}>Years Experience</span>
      </div>
      <div class={styles.highlight}>
        <span class={styles.highlightValue}>Denver, CO</span>
        <span class={styles.highlightLabel}>Based Locally</span>
      </div>
      <div class={styles.highlight}>
        <span class={styles.highlightValue}>Staff Engineer</span>
        <span class={styles.highlightSub}>@ Kasa</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class={styles.cta}>
      <Button variant="secondary" size="medium" href="/about/">More About Me</Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
